rows.label: qst200908_msg001
rows.name: Are youokay?

rows.label: qst200908_msg002
rows.name: Phew... Thanks for rescue...

rows.label: qst200908_msg003
rows.name:
Me think Kupon going to take leave
here...

rows.label: qst200908_msg004
rows.name: Hey, wait up!

rows.label: qst200908_msg005
rows.name: How come you know who I am?

rows.label: qst200908_msg007
rows.name:
K-Kupon know nothing! Not want
to think about it!

rows.label: qst200908_msg008
rows.name: So you do know something?

rows.label: qst200908_msg009
rows.name: He's babbling. I should know.

rows.label: qst200908_msg010
rows.name: Have we met before?

rows.label: qst200908_msg039
rows.name:
Okay... Kupon explain, if only to stop
things get more bad.

rows.label: qst200908_msg011
rows.name: ...It about 20 years ago now.

rows.label: qst200908_msg012
rows.name:
Kupon was discussing business deal
with Kasane and Driver.

rows.label: qst200908_msg013
rows.name: And something went wrong?

rows.label: qst200908_msg014
rows.name:
Not there. Talks went smooth,
no problem.

rows.label: qst200908_msg015
rows.name:
Problem was on way home. Just after
me say goodbye to them two.

rows.label: qst200908_msg016
rows.name:
Big boulder fall, pinning Kupon down.
Kupon squeeze out, but then ground
crumble and me fall into Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst200908_msg017
rows.name:
And just when Kupon think made it
safe back on land, it turn out to be
nest of monsters!

rows.label: qst200908_msg018
rows.name: That's, uh...

rows.label: qst200908_msg019
rows.name: Sounds like a hell of a day.

rows.label: qst200908_msg020
rows.name:
You poor thing. You had so much
bad luck...

rows.label: qst200908_msg021
rows.name: But don't you worry!

rows.label: qst200908_msg022
rows.name:
Now we're here, all that's gonna
change! It so happens we're full
to bursting with good fortune!

rows.label: qst200908_msg026
rows.name:
Uhh... Oh yeah, actually we wanted
to ask you something.

rows.label: qst200908_msg027
rows.name:
Have you seen a guy named Otto?
He was supposed to have gone to
the Nocclia Timber Site...

rows.label: qst200908_msg028
rows.name:
...Kupon know Otto. Have exchanged
hellos few times.

rows.label: qst200908_msg029
rows.name: So you know him!

rows.label: qst200908_msg030
rows.name:
But moment he left, he captured
by Tirkin and taken away.

rows.label: qst200908_msg040
rows.name: Wait, what?!

rows.label: qst200908_msg041
rows.name: That's no small matter!

rows.label: qst200908_msg031
rows.name:
He surely being held prisoner at
Tirkin Turf near Twin Trunks Hill.

rows.label: qst200908_msg032
rows.name:
Kupon never even consider that
Tirkin show up all way out here.

rows.label: qst200908_msg033
rows.name: It not safe around here any more...

rows.label: qst200908_msg034
rows.name:
Anyway, you finished asking Kupon
questions, yes? Me take leave now!

rows.label: qst200908_msg035
rows.name:
Well... Of all the things I expected,
I did not predict this.

rows.label: qst200908_msg036
rows.name:
We'd better hurry and get Otto
out of there!
